N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 309.9 - Payment of premium

State Regulations

Monthly payments of premiums for the plan shall be made to
the designated insurer upon audit and warrant of the Comptroller from funds
made available to the university for such purpose. Notes
